    <p>The syntax includes <code>.pull-one-mobile</code>, <code>.pull-two-mobile</code>, <code>.pull-three-mobile</code>, <code>.push-one-mobile</code>, <code>.push-two-mobile</code>, <code>.push-three-mobile</code>.</p>

